---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Medicare — Johnny Watts Agency" description="Learn about Medicare options with Johnny Watts Agency. Expert guidance for Medicare coverage in North Carolina.">

  <section class="bg-dark text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-white mb-3">Medicare</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg">Expert guidance through your Medicare options</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <!-- Hero image placeholder — will be replaced with R2/Sanity image -->
      <div class="w-full h-64 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg mb-8"></div>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Medicare is the federally provided healthcare insurance. Original Medicare provides for fundamental doctor and hospital costs. However, Original Medicare might not cover some expenses which can result in out-of-pocket expenses when getting treatment.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray leading-relaxed mb-6">
        To ensure that you will not be spending too much on these out-of-pocket expenses, you can get additional insurance coverage.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray leading-relaxed">
        We have extensive experience providing assistance and services to those seeking Medicare plans.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-12 bg-primary text-white text-center">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-white mb-4">Ready to Explore Your Medicare Options?</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-100 mb-6">Call us at <a href="tel:8286354200" class="text-white underline font-semibold">(828) 635-4200</a> or request a quote online.</p>
      <a href="/medicare-quote/" class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-white text-primary font-semibold rounded-md hover:bg-gray-light transition-colors">
        Get a Medicare Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
